judgment_text: COMPANY PETITION NO.823 OF 1981 OLR/11/08/CC-DII(IV) In the matter of M/s. Suri Papers & Chemicals Pvt.Ltd. Mr.M.P.Rege for Haryana Financial Corporation. Mr.S.Ramakantha, Dy. O.L. P.C. : P.C. : P.C. : 1. Perused the Official Liquidator s report dated 14th January, 2008. The same is granted in terms of prayer clause (a) without prejudice to the rights of the M/s.Haryana Financial Corporation to insist for higher claim amount which is prayed in the Company Application (L) No.88 of 2008. 2. Report disposed off on the above terms.
